nd leads to a CPN model that can support the hierarchical and compositional verification techniques that are suitable for the large-scale BPMN design models. The proposed transformation has been implemented as a transformation framework and is able to consistently transform the BPMN design models into CPN models.\",\"citedby-count\":\"29\",\"affiliation\": [{\"@_fa\": \"true\", \"affiliation-url\":\"https://api.elsevier.com/content/affiliation/affiliation_id/60028190\",\"afid\":\"60028190\",\"affilname\":\"Chulalongkorn University\",\"affiliation-city\":\"Bangkok\",\"affiliation-country\":\"Thailand\"}],\"prism:aggregationType\":\"Journal\",\"subtype\":\"ar\",\"subtypeDescription\":\"Article\",\"author-count\":{\"@limit\": \"100\", \"$\" :\"3\"},\"author\": [{\"@_fa\": \"true\", \"@seq\": \"1\", \"author-url\":\"https://api.elsevier.com/content/author/author_id/54683571200\",\"authid\":\"54683571200\",\"orcid\":\"0000-0001-8441-8962\",\"authname\":\"Dechsupa C.\",\"surname\":\"Dechsupa\",\"given-name\":\"C.\",\"initials\":\"C.\",\"afid\": [{\"@_fa\": \"true\", \"$\" :\"60028190\"}]},{\"@_fa\": \"true\", \"@seq\": \"2\", \"author-url\":\"https://api.elsevier.com/content/author/author_id/6507688023\",\"authid\":\"6507688023\",\"authname\":\"Vatanawood W.\",\"surname\":\"Vatanawood\",\"given-name\":\"W.\",\"initials\":\"W.\",\"afid\": [{\"@_fa\": \"true\", \"$\" :\"60028190\"}]},{\"@_fa\": \"true\", \"@seq\": \"3\", \"author-url\":\"https://api.elsevier.com/content/author/author_id/6507723368\",\"authid\":\"6507723368\",\"authname\":\"Thongtak A.\",\"surname\":\"Thongtak\",\"given-name\":\"A.\",\"initials\":\"A.\",\"afid\": [{\"@_fa\": \"true\", \"$\" :\"60028190\"}]}],\"authkeywords\":\"BPMN | colored Petri net | formal verification | model transformation\",\"article-number\":\"8405526\",\"source-id\":\"21100374601\",\"fund-acr\":\"CU\",\"fund-sponsor\":\"Chulalongkorn University\",\"openaccess\":\"1\",\"openaccessFlag\":true,\"freetoread\":{\"value\": [{\"$\" :\"all\